# Feature Hook Architecture

- In `src/features/**/components`, keep components focused on rendering.
- Move form/query orchestration, derived state, and submit handlers into `src/features/**/hooks`.
- Prefer one hook per screen flow (`useXxxPage`, `useXxxForm`) with explicit return shape.
- Keep API adapters in `api/`, state in `model/`, pure helpers in `lib/`.

## Pattern

```tsx
// component
const vm = useCareerJobsPage();
return <CareerJobsView {...vm} />;
```

```ts
// hook
export function useCareerJobsPage() {
  // query + mapping + handlers
  return { items, isLoading, isError };
}
```
